{"tid":1629250,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[勇武就做得啱] 分析唔同藍絲既春袋","createTime":"2019-10-06T07:43:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-06T09:23:51.000Z","uid":5564,"like":47,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"734074b9e51b729945d08fe7013b56ce24e4941f","tid":1629250,"uid":5564,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T07:43:02.000Z","msg":"出面好撚多風向post, 作為一個CD rom, 我真係屌哂你地老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我要講，根本勇武就做得啱 ！<br />\n<br />\n依家勇武做既野係完完全全對準政權既春袋, 你地望清楚唔同既藍絲持份者：<br />\n<br />\n1. 黑社會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n依家成個二坡坊跪撚低左，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">係跪撚低左啊</span></span> 根本果啲藍絲係欺善怕惡既人渣，而佢地既鋪就係佢地既春袋。你地睇下，6月既時候福建人叫福建人落黎，8月既時候係黑衣人叫福建人落黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />總之黑鋪應該裝修到佢地跪低。我強烈建議大家send跪低左相俾藍絲親戚。<br />\n<br />\n2. 商家佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n美心，360，裝修完之後發生咩事？<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">佢地跪撚低啊</span></span> 佢地無出過聲，因為佢地既鋪就係佢地既春袋啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">佢地連譴責都無譴責啊</span></span> 知唔知點解，<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">因為佢地好撚驚呀</span></span> <br />\n<br />\n3.藍絲親戚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n經過我幾個月既了解，藍絲親戚根本就係誰大誰惡誰正確。前日個黑警俾人紅燒狗肉，我同個藍絲親戚講依家有200萬黑衣人都係咁，佢地嚇到聲都唔敢出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我地要做既係<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">發放負面能量俾佢地</span></span>，話俾佢地知警察已經搞唔掂，依家政府已經到左盡頭。勝利球迷既佢地就會轉向我地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n4. 黑警<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n黑警唔駛講，個春袋就係18區開花<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />呢幾日發生咩事唔駛多講，總之，人數一多狗就搞唔掂<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />總之，<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">敵進我退，敵駐我擾，敵疲我打，敵退我追</span></span>。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n5. 林鄭/其他高官走狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢地既春依就係<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">《人權法案》</span></span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 其實佢地全部都係牆頭草，個個口講愛國，但係就有幾本passport<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 法案一過，佢地就共享大灣區光榮<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 而且，佢地既仔女都仆哂街<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 所以我地只要keep住國際既關注，相信會見到佢地有報應既一日<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n6. 中共<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">經濟就係中共既春袋</span></span>，事實上，好多外資都係經香港流入中國。其實緊急法過左之後，相信好多外資會慢慢走資<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 緊急法即係金手指，香港已經係一個rule by law 既社會，唔係法治既社會<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />當一個地方無法律保障，更加唔需要講經濟<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">If we burn, you burn with us</span></span> <br />\n<br />\n最後我想重申，<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">我係核爆都割<br />\n</span></span> 香港人加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"857efda9c1ca55128efc0b2f753aa32394e2b8c7","tid":1629250,"uid":5564,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"734074b9e51b729945d08fe7013b56ce24e4941f","tid":1629250,"uid":5564,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T07:43:02.000Z","msg":"出面好撚多風向post, 作為一個CD rom, 我真係屌哂你地老母<img src=\"/a