-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">《人權法案》</span></span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 其實佢地全部都係牆頭草，個個口講愛國，但係就有幾本passport<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 法案一過，佢地就共享大灣區光榮<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 而且，佢地既仔女都仆哂街<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 所以我地只要keep住國際既關注，相信會見到佢地有報應既一日<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n6. 中共<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">經濟就係中共既春袋</span></span>，事實上，好多外資都係經香港流入中國。其實緊急法過左之後，相信好多外資會慢慢走資<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 緊急法即係金手指，香港已經係一個rule by law 既社會，唔係法治既社會<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />當一個地方無法律保障，更加唔需要講經濟<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">If we burn, you burn with us</span></span> <br />\n<br />\n最後我想重申，<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">我係核爆都割<br />\n</span></span> 香港人加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T07:44:50.000Z","msg":"Push<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea9ee6dba8ed75a918b6d77fa2572133902d995b","tid":1629250,"uid":114154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T07:45:19.000Z","msg":"分析正確<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e5b65a36826a04922d8e731effd4a60a4da1cfa","tid":1629250,"uid":234271,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T07:46:19.000Z","msg":"裝修唔係問題<br />\n唔放火魔就得<br />\n有叢林魔法師<br />\n水系魔法師<br />\n化學魔法師<br />\n唔好搞到消防不停救火就得<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n火系魔法師宜在阻人前進以及對鬼用<br />\n民居出火 <br />\n輕則吸濃煙<br />\n中則疏散成橦大廈<br />\n重則燒死樓上住客同消防"},{"pid":"3cbf95f2cef60a991424